                        inspiration. I'm guessing a lot of developers who are not designers but who
                        love design and/or are trying to learn, felt the same way. Also, like so
                        many have mentioned, it's one of the only online spaces I've come across
                        that made me feel better, not worse. I guess this service is mainly about
                        contributing in some way to that.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        More materially, I would absolutely love it if, through this tool, I could connect
                        with more of you or if it could help you keep your profiles alive.
                    </p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
